      <title>伯克希尔旗下贷款机构因“无法负担”的贷款被消费者金融保护局起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/berkshire-owned-lender-sued-by-cfpb-over-unaffordable-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家最高金融监管机构在周一提起的诉讼中指控称，沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司旗下的一家贷款机构故意忽视部分借款人的收入或资产不足，发放了“无法承受”的住房抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/berkshire-owned-lender-sued-by-cfpb-over-unaffordable-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称，2025 年油价平均每桶 65 美元，OPEC+ 将继续承压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/oil-averaging-65-in-25-to-keep-opec-under-pressure-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，由于非欧佩克国家新增石油产量超过全球原油消费量的增长，今年国际基准布伦特原油平均价格将达到每桶 65 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/oil-averaging-65-in-25-to-keep-opec-under-pressure-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:38:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储库克称官员们在降息方面可以更加谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，鉴于劳动力市场强劲且近期通胀数据不稳定，政策制定者可以更加谨慎地采取进一步降息措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/fed-s-cook-says-officials-can-be-more-cautious-with-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比尔·杜德利谈美联储的沟通和信息传递挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/dudley-on-fed-s-communication-messaging-challenges-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前纽约联邦储备银行行长、彭博观点专栏作家、彭博经济高级顾问比尔·杜德利解释了他认为美联储在政策信息传递方面存在哪些不足，并就央行如何改善沟通提出了建议。他的观点仅代表他个人观点。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/dudley-on-fed-s-communication-messaging-challenges-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 在增加优先认购权后购买比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 宣布将使用永久优先股以及普通股和债务来购买更多加密货币，随后购买了价值 1.01 亿美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪士尼即将达成协议，将 Hulu + Live 与 Fubo 合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/disney-is-said-to-near-deal-to-merge-hulu-live-into-fubo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华特迪士尼公司和流媒体提供商 FuboTV Inc. 同意合并他们的在线直播电视业务，创建第二大数字付费电视提供商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/disney-is-said-to-near-deal-to-merge-hulu-live-into-fubo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 投资者期待黄仁勋在 CES 上的演讲能带来下一次突破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/nvidia-investors-look-to-huang-ces-speech-to-spark-next-breakout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 的投资者寄予厚望，希望首席执行官黄仁勋周一的讲话能引发该芯片制造商股价的新一轮突破。在 2024 年的大部分时间里飙升之后，该股自 11 月以来一直处于稳定状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/nvidia-investors-look-to-huang-ces-speech-to-spark-next-breakout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 10:52:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登禁止在美国大西洋和太平洋进行近海石油钻探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-bars-offshore-oil-drilling-in-us-atlantic-and-pacific</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登无限期阻止在美国沿海超过 6.25 亿英亩的水域进行海上石油和天然气开发，并警告说，在那里钻探根本“不值得冒险”并且“没有必要”满足国家的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-bars-offshore-oil-drilling-in-us-atlantic-and-pacific</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普言论令美元迅速缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示不会削减关税政策计划后，美元迅速缩减跌幅。大型科技股上涨提振了股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
